We gratefully acknowledge the work of The Document Foundation and
all LibreOffice contributors.

VNOffice modifications include:
- Rebranding (name, logo, splash screen, icons)
- Vietnamese language as default
- Vietnamese document templates
- Vietnamese default settings (A4 paper, margins, date format)
- Additional Vietnamese fonts

